    <h1>302 Redirect</h1>
    <p class="description">A temporary HTTP status code that sends visitors to another URL while telling search engines the original URL will return. Google keeps the original URL in its index and holds ranking signals there.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
